WEBVTT

00:00.377 --> 00:02.782
ï»¿"Much" is used for uncountable nouns...

00:03.109 --> 00:05.675
...while "many" is used for countable nouns.

00:07.860 --> 00:09.275
How much money do you want?

00:11.717 --> 00:13.318
She doesn't have much money.

00:16.341 --> 00:17.926
How much time does he have?

00:18.275 --> 00:19.832
He doesn't have much time.

00:23.446 --> 00:24.777
How many people are there?

00:25.415 --> 00:26.543
There are many men.

00:29.609 --> 00:31.301
How much meat do you want?

00:31.505 --> 00:32.117
Not much.

00:35.378 --> 00:37.341
How many hamburgers can you eat?

00:37.605 --> 00:38.500
A lot, please.

